1997;;Never Too Late;;Canadian;;Giles Walker;;Olympia Dukakis, Cloris Leachman;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Never_Too_Late_(1997_film);;Joseph, Rose and Olive suspect Carl, the owner of a retirement home, of misusing the funds of the home's residents. Together they set out to see that no one takes advantage of their unhealthy friend Woody.